:::the ships hit the water and then hit a ledge of the under water mountain. 
Herald hops out of the ship and sets up the water tight gate at entrance to 
the main cave. Tran, data, Defect, andHerald begin to carry the equipment 
into the now dry under water mountain caves. defection looks into the ship to 
make sure they had gotten every thing. he sees gigatron.

Defection: "Gigatron come on in the cave its dry now and no water will get in 
with the new water tight gate. come in all your stuffs there already"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Herald looked around at his new lab and got right to work.

Tran and Data started working on angels again.
